{"tid":507260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重案男警加控7項爆竊罪","createTime":"2017-12-23T04:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T04:57:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9429f53a585aece256172bce3036f5d4cd4c947d","tid":507260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253116&d=YMjKz3cQ%2Fky9YqE0tBko1r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cc18503f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F20253116&h=4a79cc78\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171223/20253116</a><br />\n<br />\n重案男警加控7項爆竊罪<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171223/large/14605443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171223%2Flarge%2F14605443.jpg&h=ff7cefce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】西九龍總區重案組男警涉嫌知法犯法，在停職受查期間，半個月內三度偷竊奶粉及藥物，因而被控。案件昨日再訊，控方披露原來涉案男警於過去兩年間另涉7次爆竊不同食店，被加控7項爆竊罪。案件下月19日再提堂，等候轉介區域法院文件，男警繼續還柙候訊。<br />\n<br />\n新增控罪指被告陳曉健（34歲）於前年4月至今年1月間，先後爆竊荃灣小紅館、觀塘香城冰室、紅磡冰室、元朗潮城魚蛋粉等，偷去共10.2萬元現金及財物。被告早前被控3項盜竊罪，指他於今年9月18至28日間，兩度在屯門工業中心地下升降機大堂偷竊共264罐奶粉，總值5.5萬元等。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC2645/17<br />\n■記者羅日昇、楊家樂"}]}